OVERVIEW
As an AI Designer / Motion Designer at Shuttlerock, you will combine strong design skills with the ability to integrate AI into the creative process. You’ll help shape visual storytelling from concept to motion, using AI platforms to accelerate production and traditional tools to refine and finalize assets.
In this role, you will generate visuals with AI tools, polish and compose them into static or animated content, and bring them to life in motion. Working closely with Art Directors, 3D Designers and sound engineers, you will ensure projects are consistent, innovative and delivered at the highest standard.

Your responsibilities will include:
• creating concept visuals, style frames, moodboards, and branded assets;
• using AI tools such as Runway, Adobe Firefly or Google Labs (Veo/Whisk) to rapidly generate and iterate ideas;
• compositing AI-generated outputs with Photoshop, Illustrator, After Effects and other traditional tools to achieve polished results.
You will also:
• animate short-form videos adapted to multiple platforms;
• stay ahead of AI and design trends;
• test new workflows;
• share best practices with the team.
Finally, you will ensure brand consistency across all creative outputs.

